sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval<br/>Operator
    participant Job as lm-evaluation-harness<br/>Kubernetes Job
    participant ConfigMap as /meta/job.json<br/>ConfigMap
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Serving Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Job: Flow 1: EvalHub Benchmark Execution

    Operator->>Job: Create Kubernetes Job<br/>(K8s API, ServiceAccount auth)
    Job->>ConfigMap: Read job specification<br/>(filesystem mount)
    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    Job->>HF: GET tokenizers, datasets<br/>HF_TOKEN Bearer, TLS 1.2+
    HF-->>Job: Tokenizer & dataset artifacts

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+

    loop For each evaluation sample (concurrent up to 128)
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>OPENAI_API_KEY Bearer, TLS 1.2+
        Model-->>Job: Completion response (JSON)
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    Note over Job: Compute metrics<br/>(accuracy, F1, ROUGE, etc.)

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
    Job->>OCI: Push evaluation results<br/>Registry credentials, TLS 1.2+
    Job->>MLflow: Log metrics & run metadata<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>+ evaluation results<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Operator,MLflow: Flow 2: Offline / Disconnected Evaluation

    participant S3 as S3 / IBM COS<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant InitC as Init Container
    participant SharedVol as /test_data<br/>Shared Volume

    Operator->>InitC: Create init container
    InitC->>S3: Download datasets & tokenizers<br/>AWS IAM / IBM COS creds, TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>InitC: Dataset artifacts
    InitC->>SharedVol: Write to /test_data
    InitC-->>Job: Init container completes

    Note over Job: Set HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_EVALUATE_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1<br/>HF_HOME=/test_data

    Job->>SharedVol: Read datasets & tokenizers<br/>(filesystem)

    loop For each evaluation sample
        Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>OPENAI_API_KEY Bearer, TLS 1.2+
        Model-->>Job: Completion response
    end

    Job->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETED<br/>+ evaluation results<br/>Bearer Token, TLS 1.2+
